<body>
  <main class="container" style="padding-top: 4rem;">
    <h1>WE KEEP HANDS ALIVE.</h1>
    <p>Monumental. Decorative. Applied.<br>In a digital age, we still believe in fire, metal, glass, and enamel.</p>

    <div style="margin: 6rem 0; max-width: 600px;">
      <h2>THE SECTION</h2>
      <p>We don’t just preserve craft. We ignite it.</p>
      <p>Active since the Soviet era — but make it art, not propaganda.</p>
      <p>Our artists: enamel alchemists, ceramic rebels, metal whisperers.</p>
      <p>We argue about tradition over cheap tea. You should join.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 6rem 0;">
      <h2>KEY PROJECTS</h2>
      <p><strong>«IMPOSSIBLE ART»</strong><br>Where optics meet enamel. Moscow meets Tokyo.</p>
      <p><strong>«ENAMEL UNDER FIRE»</strong><br>20 artists. 400°C. One mission: prove craft is not dead.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><a href="/en/projects" style="text-decoration: underline;">→ See all projects</a></p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 6rem 0;">
      <h2>CHAIR</h2>
      <img src="https://tcxp.ru/sites/default/files/section_cnairmans/_7.jpg" alt="Evgeny Matko" style="width: 120px; height: 120px; object-fit: cover; float: left; margin-right: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;" />
      <p><strong>EUGENE MATKO</strong></p>
      <p>Chair / Enamel Alchemist / Ex-Stroganov Rebel</p>
      <p>Failed to become a mural painter. Succeeded in turning molten glass into national heritage.<br>Collects Soviet-era enamel pins. Rumored to speak to kilns in Russian.</p>
      <p><a href="https://artmatko.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">→ His private archive</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="container" style="padding: 4rem 0; border-top: 1px solid #000; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
    <p>
      <a href="/en/">HOME</a> · 
      <a href="/en/projects">PROJECTS</a> · 
      <a href="/en/contact">GET IN TOUCH</a>
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #555;">© Union of Russian Artists. Section of MDAI. {new Date().getFullYear()}</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
